description:
boto 2.34.0 was Released: 23-Oct-2014  (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/boto/2.34.0) and appears to be causing the stacktrace below:

http://logs.openstack.org/11/130611/3/check/check-tempest-dsvm-full/e57c98f/console.html#_2014-10-23_20_02_16_391

error: http://paste.openstack.org/show/123749

Since boto 2.34.0 has only been out for a few hours its too early to tell if this is the cause or not.

Query: message:"boto/connection.py" AND message:"get_list" AND filename:"console.html"
